			<div class="content" id="post-content-1364224">
									

<p>I'm not convinced the SCPs would win that easily. 939 in particular is just a random animal with a couple combat-irrelevant abilities that's fairly hard to put down. I wouldn't necessarily back it in a fight against a lion, much less a Gyrados. Only 075 and 457 strike me as really being able to shred the competition, and even then, there's still things they could lose to pretty handily. Pokemon-verse is medium high powered.</p>

