			<div class="content" id="post-content-1364245">
									

<p>Wizards. Also Crunch is Base 80 Power.</p>
<p>I put Thunder Fang in there because at that point I had two choices; keep the team as it was, or retcon in an Electric Sheep. Not only was I nearly done the entire story when I got to that point, but an Electric Sheep / Mareep-Flaaffy-Ampharos joke is&#8230; just too easy. Besides, I can totally see a Pokemon 939 having Thunder/Ice/Fire Fangs as at least Move Tutor moves, if not learned naturally in its 20s. It's stated in-article to kill with a single bite to the back of the head. 939 are also ~9 foot tall and 500 pounds of predatory muscle.</p>

